The Beijing Meteorological Observatory announced at 11: 00 on the 26th that there were scattered showers (accompanied by weak lightning) in Beijing on the 26th, and the daily maximum temperature was only 27 ℃; the night was overcast with light to moderate rain (accompanied by weak lightning), and the minimum temperature at night was 23 ℃.
