In terms of the physical and mental health of minors, the draft for comments proposes that the sale of alcoholic beverages to minors is prohibited, and the location of alcoholic beverages is restricted. For violations of the regulations, the market supervision and administration department will order corrections and impose a fine of 30,000 yuan.
