" In midsummer, Qinghai Lake is full of golden flowers and thousands of bees flying. Here, the altitude is higher, the temperature difference between day and night is large, and the air pollution is less. The strong light breeds the most tenacious and generous bee colony, creating Qinghai royal jelly with high activity, high protein, rich nutritional value, low sugar and low fat characteristics. "
