The picture shows the sea of rape flowers by Qinghai Lake.
This spring, due to the need to set up road barriers for epidemic prevention and control, the way of beekeepers " chasing flowers and honey " was blocked. Many bees died due to missed flowering and lack of food, and the income of beekeepers was seriously affected.
