Nowadays, the number of beekeepers is decreasing. In addition to beekeepers who travel all the year round, there are still many poor households with mobility difficulties who choose to use beehives to invest in cooperatives.
" The state has financial support. We contact technical personnel for help and guidance. Beekeepers lack understanding and judgment of the market environment. To open a market, they also need the help and coordination of the government, enterprises, and industry associations. "
Zhao Xiaochuan said.
" I hope everyone will pay more attention to and help beekeepers in the future" , Wu Na said. " Our bee products are also screened and controlled in strict accordance with national standards to ensure quality and protect consumer rights while helping beekeepers. "
